data.title: Save-On-Foods Memorial Centre
data.text:
Explore the City of Victoria's fall 2024 recreation programs! Discover our fall program guides on August 6 and reconnect with your favourite activities. Registration opens on August 19 at 7 a.m. for all fall programs, including skating and on August 21 at 7 a.m. for swimming programs.
